officialTitle: Assessment of and Treatment Applied to Food Addiction to Encourage Self-Management of Obesity in a Rural Healthy Behaviors Clinic
inclusionCriteria:
* Overweight/Obese Adult patients (age 19 years -65)
* eligible based on WALI screening tool
* Must have minimum age of 19 Years
* Must have maximum age of 65 Years
exclusionCriteria:
* Inability to understand and read English.
* Women pregnant or lactating.
* persons with terminal illness
